articles.author: Ethan Shanfeld
articles.title: Oasis Announces North American Tour Dates - Variety
articles.description: Liam and Noel Gallagher will bring their Oasis reunion tour to North America.
articles.content:
Oasis is officially coming to North America next year on its highly anticipated reunion tour.
